<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q15_v6" title="Q15_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Una familia registra mensualmente el consumo de electricidad de su casa, medido en kilowatt-hora (kWh).</p>
    <p>En mayo el consumo fue de 178,6 kWh y en junio fue de 192,45 kWh. 
    
Según estos datos, ¿cuál de las siguientes cantidades corresponde al aumento de consumo desde mayo a junio?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">1,385<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El aumento se obtiene restando 192,45 − 178,6 = 13,85. Por lo tanto, 1,385 no corresponde al aumento de consumo desde mayo a junio.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">13,85<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El aumento de consumo desde mayo a junio es 192,45 − 178,6 = 13,85. Por eso, la cantidad correcta es 13,85 kWh.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">0,1385<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El aumento se obtiene restando 192,45 − 178,6 = 13,85. Por lo tanto, 0,1385 no corresponde al aumento de consumo desde mayo a junio.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">14,05<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El aumento correcto es 192,45 − 178,6 = 13,85. Como 14,05 es distinto de 13,85, esa cantidad no corresponde al aumento de consumo.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar qué pide el problema</strong></p>
            <p>Se pide el aumento de consumo desde mayo a junio. Un aumento se calcula restando el valor inicial al valor final.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Escribir los datos</strong></p>
            <p>Mayo:
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mn>178,6</mn>
              </math>
              kWh
            </p>
            <p>Junio:
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mn>192,45</mn>
              </math>
              kWh
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Restar junio menos mayo</strong></p>
            <p>Para restar con decimales, se alinean las comas decimales:</p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <mn>192,45</mn>
                  <mo>−</mo>
                  <mn>178,60</mn>
                  <mo>=</mo>
                  <mn>13,85</mn>
                </mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Interpretar el resultado</strong></p>
            <p>El consumo aumentó en
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mn>13,85</mn>
              </math>
              kWh.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es
              <strong>B</strong>:
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mn>13,85</mn>
              </math>.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>